    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Form::addSubForm() expects a 'name' argument. However, this argument is not used to set the name of the SubForm. Unless the subForm has a name already set, Zend_Form should immediately call setName() on the newly added SubForm.</p>

